Gaston Michel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaston_Michel 0 Gaston Michel (1856 - November 1921) was a French silent film actor. He starred in some 40 films between 1913 and his death in 1921. He died in November 1921, in Lisbon, Portugal. Gaston_Michel ( 1856 - November 1921 ) was a_French_silent_film_actor . He starred in some_40_films between 1913 and his_death in 1921 . He died in November_1921 , in Lisbon , Portugal .
